            "questionText": "What is the value of i^4n+1, where n is an integer?",
            "options": [
              "1",
              "-1",
              "i",
              "-i",
              "0"
            ],
            "correctOptionIndex": 2
          },
          "explanation": {
            "text": "We know the powers of i repeat in a cycle of 4: i, -1, -i, 1.\n\ni^(4n+1) = (i^4n) * i^1\nSince i^4n = (i^4)^n = 1^n = 1\n\nThe result is 1 * i = i.",
