            "questionText": "If z = 3 + 4i, what is the modulus |z|?",
            "options": [
              "3",
              "4",
              "5",
              "7",
              "25"
            ],
            "correctOptionIndex": 2
          },
          "explanation": {
            "text": "The modulus of a complex number z = x + iy is given by sqrt(x^2 + y^2).\n\n|z| = sqrt(3^2 + 4^2)\n|z| = sqrt(9 + 16)\n|z| = sqrt(25) = 5.",
